    "Blend the main detail pane into the sidebar with a soft boundary fade." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "用柔和的过渡把主详情区与侧边栏融合。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anthropic's API re-reports the cached context on every assistant turn, so the same tokens get counted many times. Turn off to show only “new” traffic (input + output + cache writes). Estimated cost is unaffected." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Anthropic 的 API 每次助手回合都会把缓存上下文重新上报，所以同一批 token 会被反复计数。关闭后只显示「新增」流量（输入 + 输出 + 缓存写入），费用估算不受影响。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "API estimate uses standard first-party token prices. Detailed billing also applies fast mode and web search charges when Claude logs expose them." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API 估算使用官方标准 token 单价。详细账单会在 Claude 日志显式记录时,额外计入 fast 模式与 web search 的费用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Where API Provider Switcher saves provider keys. JSON keeps them with provider data; Keychain stores references in the library." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "API Provider Switcher 保存密钥的位置。JSON 把密钥与平台数据放在一起;Keychain 则把引用保存在系统钥匙串。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Shows selected Claude service health on the Dashboard. Alerts only monitor the components shown here." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在 Dashboard 显示已选的 Claude 服务健康状况。提醒只针对这里展示的组件。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Adds an Activity tab that compares coding surfaces, CLI hosts, and AI activity. Reading Screen Time requires Full Disk Access." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "增加一个「活动」标签页,对比编码界面、CLI 宿主与 AI 活动。读取「屏幕使用时间」需要完整磁盘访问权限。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Turn it on in Features to edit Screen Time access and coding surface settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在「功能」中打开此项,即可编辑屏幕使用时间访问与编码界面设置。"
